---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
	<div class="section gap-y-20 py-32">
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<div class="col-span-full text-center px-4">
			<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-6">The Network That Funds You</h1>
			<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/70 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				ChainFlow V2 is no longer just a prop trading firm. It's a new type of on-chain protocol where the network provides the capital and users are free to build, trade, invest, and experiment without auditions, upfront costs, or arbitrary restrictions.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Core Trading Features -->
		<div class="col-span-full px-4">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Core Network Features</h2>
			<p class="text-white/60 text-center mb-12">Protocol-level capital for builders, traders, and on-chain operators</p>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
				<!-- Feature 1 -->
				<div class="feature-card p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur">
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-400">Network-level funding</span>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Smart Wallets Funded by the Protocol</h3>
					<p class="text-white/70 mb-6">
						Every user receives a ChainFlow smart wallet that is funded directly by the network, not a single prop account. Use it to deploy apps, trade on any on-chain protocol, provide liquidity, or invest — all actions are settled transparently on Paxeer and OpenNet.
					</p>
					<a href="https://explorer.opennet.paxeer.app" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors">
						View OpenNet Explorer →
					</a>
				</div>

				<!-- Feature 2 -->
				<div class="feature-card p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur">
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400">Community capital</span>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Community Funding Pools</h3>
					<p class="text-white/70">
						All capital comes from community funding pools in ETH and OP, backed by 1.5B USD worth of collateralized staked PAX coins. The protocol routes this capital across users and strategies, allowing anyone to access meaningful size without raising their own funds.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Feature 3 -->
				<div class="feature-card p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur">
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-purple-400">Multi-surface</span>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Trade, Build, Invest — One Stack</h3>
					<p class="text-white/70">
						ChainFlow is not limited to trading challenges. Use your funded smart wallet to ship apps, deploy strategies, trade spot or derivatives, provide liquidity, or experiment with new protocols — all under the same network-level capital model.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Feature 4 -->
				<div class="feature-card p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur">
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-yellow-400">No auditions</span>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">No Fees, No Auditions, No Profit Targets</h3>
					<p class="text-white/70">
						There are no evaluation fees, no drawdown rules, no profit targets, and no challenges to pass. Users simply connect, use their smart wallet as they normally would, and the protocol handles risk and payouts in the background.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Feature 5 -->
				<div class="feature-card p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur">
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-emerald-400">Algorithmic payouts</span>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">LLM-Powered Risk & Payout Engine</h3>
					<p class="text-white/70">
						A proprietary network-wide algorithm tracks each funded smart wallet using over 500 on-chain and behavioral data points. LLMs and risk models work together to decide when and how much a user can withdraw, turning normal on-chain behavior into automated, transparent payouts.
					</p>
				</div>

				<!-- Feature 6 -->
				<div class="feature-card p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur">
					<div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
						<span class="text-sm font-bold text-cyan-400">Open infrastructure</span>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">OpenNet + Paxeer Mainnet</h3>
					<p class="text-white/70 mb-6">
						OpenNet and Paxeer mainnet form the execution layer for the protocol. Builders and traders operate on public ledgers while the ChainFlow network handles funding, risk, and settlement logic at the protocol level.
					</p>
					<a href="https://paxscan.io" target="_blank" class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors">
						View Paxscan Explorer →
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Social Features -->
		<div class="col-span-full px-4 mt-20">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Social & Community Features</h2>
			<p class="text-white/60 text-center mb-12">A global community of funded builders, traders, and on-chain operators</p>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
				<div class="social-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent backdrop-blur">
					<span class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2 block">Network-native</span>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Public Network Chatrooms</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-white/70">
						Discuss app ideas, trading strategies, investment theses, and protocol integrations with other funded users. Everything revolves around the same network capital rails.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="social-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent backdrop-blur">
					<span class="text-xs font-bold text-green-400 mb-2 block">Military-grade encryption</span>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">End-to-End Encrypted DMs</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-white/70">
						Collaborate with other funded users in private. Coordinate product launches, share alpha, or design strategies knowing your conversations stay fully encrypted.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="social-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent backdrop-blur">
					<span class="text-xs font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2 block">Build your brand</span>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Public On-Chain Profiles</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-white/70">
						Showcase how you use the network: trades, apps, pools, and payouts — all surfaced through your smart wallet history. Build a public track record as a builder, trader, or investor.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="social-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent backdrop-blur">
					<span class="text-xs font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2 block">Free & Premium</span>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Strategy & Signals Channels</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-white/70">
						Share and monetize strategies that span trading, yield, and app flows. Signal providers and builders can earn from the same protocol that funds their wallets.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="social-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent backdrop-blur">
					<span class="text-xs font-bold text-emerald-400 mb-2 block">Zero slippage</span>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">P2P Deals & Liquidity</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-white/70">
						Match with other funded users for OTC deals, liquidity partnerships, and JV-style structures — all recorded and settled on-chain.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="social-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent backdrop-blur">
					<span class="text-xs font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-2 block">Learn & Build</span>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Education & Network Playbooks</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-white/70">
						Access playbooks on how to best use your funded smart wallet: from trading and yield to product launches. Learn how the risk engine scores behavior and how to maximize long-term payouts.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- CTA Section -->
		<div class="col-span-full px-4 text-center mt-20">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Let the Network Fund You?</h2>
			<p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				Join ChainFlow V2, receive a funded smart wallet, and use it however you operate best on-chain. No auditions, no fees, no profit targets — just the protocol handling capital, risk, and payouts for you.
			</p>
			<div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
				<a href="https://dashboard.paxeer.app/en" target="_blank" class="px-8 py-3 bg-white text-black rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors">
					Get Your Funded Wallet
				</a>
				<a href="/about" class="px-8 py-3 border border-white/20 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
					Learn More About ChainFlow V2
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.feature-card, .social-card {
		transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
	}
	
	.feature-card:hover, .social-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
	}
</style>
